{"tid":212371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支唔支持默認器官捐贈？","createTime":"2017-04-22T11:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T06:41:10.000Z","uid":25038,"like":69,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e177b57bfeb4899568928184a7e814f6b5a39a58","tid":212371,"uid":25038,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"In case你唔明，<br />\n默認器官捐贈啫係你唔去出聲反對嘅話，<br />\n死咗之後就要捐贈器官<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反對"},{"pid":"3618eb46d001facdf7e18ca1cf29e91d247865cf","tid":212371,"uid":71000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:20:36.000Z","msg":"其實冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  新加坡係好例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12d31e2f2eb7a1e71620e2da5380a1f6fd22723","tid":212371,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:21:16.000Z","msg":"默許即刻昆d無知婦孺既器官走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2633d64a849d3b907d980c240aee46a144853091","tid":212371,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"一句:我地無收到你反對既申請喎就捐撚左去"},{"pid":"c026e321b0551153ecb9d8a41ba074d1cdc8b39c","tid":212371,"uid":27108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n反正我實會簽不同意書<br />\n等班唔關心時事政治既港豬捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e6053af3b0b07a19b0b489f3cb94f9f4568756","tid":212371,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持<br />\n反正我實會簽不同意書<br />\n等班唔關心時事政治既港豬捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打點解唔想捐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3873ded2b26707cbb5743567e75a